text: Aachhat is a village located in Girwa Tehsil of Udaipur district in the Indian state of Rajasthan. As per Population Census 2011, Aachhat village has population of 211 of which 105 are males while 106 are females. It is administrated by Sarpanch (Head of Village) who is elected representative of village. == References == Category:Villages in Udaipur district
title: Aachhat
